{"tid":1080653,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"開發左4年既ff7 remake終於有新消息","createTime":"2019-03-27T17:42:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T03:32:15.000Z","uid":173952,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4ffd28084b6376311fdc84aadac81f79f7b15b0c","tid":1080653,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T17:42:01.000Z","msg":"最終幻想7》的複刻版已於昨日正式上線，不過已經讓玩家等待多年的《最終幻想7：重製版》卻遲遲不見新消息公佈，而近日，外媒爆料SE或將於4月舉行發布會，公佈《最終幻想7：重製版》的新情報。<br />\n<br />\n根據近日爆料網站4cahn爆料的情報，SE將會在4月舉行一場特別發布會，屆時官方將公開《最終幻想7：重製版》最新情報，不過目前該消息尚未經過SE證實，玩家只能先耐心等待SE發布的官方通知。<br />\n<br />\n《最終幻想7：重製版》自2015年在E3上公佈已過去了4年，然而目前為止至遊戲所公佈的情報還少得可憐，而且按照目前的進度來看，就算SE會在4月公佈新情報，距離遊戲的發售日應該還有非常長的時間"},{"pid":"7db994b7fa64c2501e507d10eb93600ca6cdaae2","tid":1080653,"uid":115082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T00:48:01.000Z","msg":"宣布改爲PS5遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0131aec25cbc9561c873f9d60c7939b484b112ff","tid":1080653,"uid":47311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T00:49:05.000Z","msg":"整10年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44287659cdcedfe895208e94d590555f853ecc57","tid":1080653,"uid":91833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T03:17:30.000Z","msg":"啲畫面由頸靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />變 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />ps3 畫面"},{"pid":"51a35ac420700492b4c24eae658f5e2f94efe53b","tid":1080653,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T03:24:21.000Z","msg":"宣佈請到人負責開發了~"},{"pid":"9fac718dec181b2c4bf958e467750f8ad5d582e9","tid":1080653,"uid":67454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T03:39:03.000Z","msg":"宣佈中止開發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"889bfe45a515e654ef89c76998fa05de73a05c68","tid":1080653,"uid":55941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci